ww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BQ6CFDCX" class="rapid-with-clickid">英特尔酷睿 i5-13500</a>降至 210 美元，比该芯片的正常价格低约 40 美元，创历史新低。对于更强大的产品， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:72;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASt2hUcAx65gYoSanqtWFZmm1bPTLjvxugFvr-q52i5G&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BQ6CSY9C%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Core i7-13700F</a>的新低价为 330 美元，比一般零售价低约 40 美元。以该价格，这在游戏和生产力方面表现出色；请注意，它缺少集成 GPU。同时，如果您更喜欢 AMD 版本， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:73;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATW_5xMG9aPOEA3iJZDCFEg0n-F2jWDwqpt904Efdu8W&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BBHHT8LY%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26psc%3D1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Ryzen 7 7700X</a>可能值得一看，价格为 297 美元。它的价值<a data-i13n="cpos:74;pos:1" href="https://cpu.userbenchmark.com/Compare/Intel-Core-i7-13700F-vs-AMD-Ryzen-7-7700X/m1997481vs4131">不如</a>i7-13700F，尤其是因为<a data-i13n="cpos:75;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amd-ryzen-7000-cpu-models-leak-193730652.html">它需要</a>AM5 主板和 DDR5 RAM 才能工作，但如果您必须拥有 Ryzen PC，它仍然是游戏的可靠中档选择。</p><h2> <strong>Dashlane Premium 特卖</strong></h2><p><core-commerce id="64d86bc441764d95b8206bf3db5c1a35" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>密码管理器是一种简单但有效的方法，可以<a data-i13n="cpos:76;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-08-26-the-best-password-managers-compared.html">提高您的在线安全性</a>并简化您需要记住的登录凭据数量。 Dashlane 是可用的更好选择之一；事实上，它很快就会成为即将发布的购买指南中的一个选择。如果您想尝试这项服务，结账时使用代码<strong>MEMDAY23</strong>或<strong>MEMORIAL23</strong>即可以 30 美元的价格获得一年的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:77;pos:1" h