netflix-starts-charging-for-account-sharing-in-the-us-185133792.html">帐户共享</a>。</p><p>谷歌去年年底宣布，它获得了从 2023 赛季开始面向住宅用户的周日门票的独家权利。 DirecTV 仍然是商业用途的周日票务提供商，例如在酒吧和餐馆。</p><p><ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/youtubes-nfl-sunday-ticket-packages-start-at-249-174949489.html">2023 赛季 NFL 周日门票套餐</a></ins>6 月 6 日之前注册的 YouTube TV 订阅者收费 249 美元。对于非 YouTube 电视订阅者、那些等到 6 月 6 日之后的订阅者以及想要访问 NFL RedZone 的人来说，它会花费更多。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/youtube-will-allow-unlimited-simultaneous-streams-for-nfl-sunday-ticket-142049241.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/youtube-will-allow-unlimited-simultaneous-streams-for-nfl-sunday-ticket-142049241.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 20724e90-0d78-4b04-aa62-a5c41d2f0492</guid><dc:creator>克里斯霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 14:20:49 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685110850</ingested><modified> 2023-05-26T14:20:54+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[American Football]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sports & Recreation]]></category><category><![CDATA[National Football League]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2592" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/3b6f70e0-fbcd-11ed-bdf7-3fd3d7391f95" width="3888"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2592" medium="image" url="https